metadata.description: **PUBLIC MINTING IS LIVE NOW: https://basc.club.** *Become a BASC member for only .12 ETH.* BASC is a set of 10,000 Bored Ape NFTs inspired by the original BAYC collection. Each colorful, AI-pixelated NFT is a one-of-a-kind collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain. Your Superpixel Bored Ape also serves as your Club membership card, granting you access to exclusive benefits for Club members.
